# hatch-pip-compile

hatch plugin to use pip-compile to manage project dependencies

[![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/hatch-pip-compile?color=blue&label=üî®%20hatch-pip-compile)](https://github.com/juftin/hatch-pip-compile)
